{
  "stem": "5644.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 200,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the men, which got a name Janek, got a birthday, like, a party.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 200,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now when I came in home-- it's a very important thing-- when I came in to that girl, she opened the door, and she said Janek, how are you?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 200,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I shouldn't be there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 200,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I should be sitting in my home and waiting for my guests.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 200,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's something very unusual.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 200,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And 20 people looking at my face, and that was no good.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 200,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I immediately felt very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 200,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That they may smell something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 201,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That I am Jan, and I am coming there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 201,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she was very smart, again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 201,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She's seen what she did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 201,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she bent down to one of the boys and start-- told them something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 201,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the word came across, around in one second, like a flash.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 201,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they all got up with glasses of vodka, took up and started to sing 100 years, 100 years, to live as long, Janek.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 201,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I start to cry because-- [CRYING] sorry for this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 202,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They sang the song.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 202,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She said to them after when it's happened, and I went, she told me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 202,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said to him that I am a boy from the forest, that I'm an Underground boy, a Christian.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 203,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But partisan.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 203,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for them a Janek Partisan got nowhere to go anyhow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 203,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he's coming anywhere he wants to, and he got a friend.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 203,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That doesn't mean for me any party anything because he got to find a place because he got his home is the--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 204,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the forest.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 204,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they sang, and they start to talk to me friendly and nice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 204,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the end of it when I get out of the problem.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 204,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I thought that I'm--",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
